# IJT CSharp Client — Cursor Rules

Read [`docs/SKILLS.md`](docs/SKILLS.md) for full project context before doing any work.

It covers: project structure, Softing OPC UA SDK integration, NuGet package versioning, test patterns, DI setup, and common mistakes.

## Critical hygiene rules (always apply)

- **Generated files**: `Types/` is auto-generated from UA-ModelCompiler — never edit, never format, never run any tool against it.
- **Pre-commit**: hooks auto-fix formatting/CRLF. If commit is rejected, run `git add -u && git commit` once more.
- See [`docs/SKILLS.md`](../../../docs/SKILLS.md) for full developer setup and hygiene details.
